{"tid":173868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參加荒野求生實境秀 10人苦撐1年才知停播","createTime":"2017-03-26T12:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T04:25:28.000Z","uid":53379,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"256289826ba5f7c03fd1faf5fa63081a27676be9","tid":173868,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">參加荒野求生實境秀 10人苦撐1年才知停播</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net/images/2017/03/26/14905007526671ng2XnyyIvK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd17ixjpazu3j94.cloudfront.net%2Fimages%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F14905007526671ng2XnyyIvK.jpg&h=e39486f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近幾年掀起一股「電視真人實境秀」熱潮，各國都不斷推出類似節目吸引觀眾眼球。英國去年3月拍攝一檔野外求生實境秀，23名參賽者被送往蘇格蘭高地一處偏遠海灣，挑戰一整年與世隔絕的生活，沒想到收視率差，播出4集就被腰斬，而苦苦撐完一整年的參賽者，直到回歸都市後才發現節目竟然早就停播。<br />\n<br />\n壯闊美景加上懸疑氣氛，這是英國第四頻道去年3月開拍的真人實境秀節目「伊甸園」，23位參賽者和4位劇組人員前進偏遠蘇格蘭高地，挑戰整整一年過著荒野求生，與世隔絕的原始生活，而且完全不能與外界聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n參賽者們認真建造這個自給自足的現代烏托邦，不過慘的不是在野外碰到各種難題，而是節目竟然播了4集就被腰斬，所有人卻都被蒙在鼓裡。據了解，原來節目去年7月首播，前四集收視就像自由落體般，從170萬人滑落到只剩80萬人，慘淡收視讓高層決定停播。<br />\n<br />\n有參賽者的親戚表示，節目方向不清、編排無聊，宣傳也沒盡力，觀眾期待出現衝突打架、愛恨情仇的戲碼，結果一票人就只是平淡的生活著，有13人因為無法適應中途退出，10人咬牙苦撐到最後，回到都市才發現，不但節目早就掰掰，整個世界還都風雲變色，這些參賽者完全不知道英國要脫歐了，也不曉得英國首相是哪位，更沒想到川普已經當上美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n對這起烏龍事件，電視台發言人解釋，之後的集數，會盡量想辦法在電視上播出，不會讓大家在野外白忙一場，只是對參賽者來說，心情真的是無奈到最高點。<br />\n<br />\n▼（影片／Youtube／Channel 4）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jqdR_WgcwbM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjqdR_WgcwbM&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c2bc809f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jqdR_WgcwbM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=56961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.news.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D56961&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8604d2ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=56961</a>"},{"pid":"634b13954a7ea3325cfa5f4b6cedb33ea2b03585","tid":173868,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"改造笑片"},{"pid":"6c985de05aae4f1b958fc76b4522d843a36d2f25","tid":173868,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"真正既精彩人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfa6e1c9fe69d507e5debf6b8b016b9395ad623","tid":173868,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"真係好真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314ec007c0ce34bdd9b6bef023f8d3ef0d8dca1b","tid":173868,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"316e9e652ab2b3057719aec65fc3187df209cb4a","tid":173868,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"點解停播左仲唔叫佢地番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875bbf38f353ca4a7f6968832e38ff164cecfdfc","tid":173868,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"荒野求生實境喜劇"},{"pid":"8c0851a8c6564bdf9073047661559ba4c81931e2","tid":173868,"uid":73412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"連工作人員都唔知停播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c89f4797ff67cb6fcc5e5f573b2168407d3eae3","tid":173868,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"英國版鏗鏘集：離開世外桃源之後&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac14ddb52828d50c08c20f32041e9b08ecbb862e","tid":173868,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"<